{"tid":1215720,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"突發 城大生被捕","createTime":"2019-06-13T08:02:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-13T08:06:26.000Z","uid":5749,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c864abfe9afef99be2368b720f5a8e1db49b3d23","tid":1215720,"uid":5749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T08:02:26.000Z","msg":"城大學生會：一名示威學生在醫院求醫時被捕<br />\n<br />\n城市大學學生會確認，一名城大學生參與反對修訂《逃犯條例》示威後被捕。城大學生會表示，該名學生當日受傷求醫，於醫院被捕，城大學生會已派出律師支援，目前有待了解進一步情況。<br />\n<br />\n2019-06-13 15:56:12<br />\n<br />\nSource rthk"},{"pid":"09d93bdefe5e3e940185944a367ac3c95247236a","tid":1215720,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":21,"score":-21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T08:05:17.000Z","msg":"希望只係個asso 仔啦<br />\n<br />\n大學生留案底就乜前途都無晒"},{"pid":"ae42708251923812f02a49f37943cf82c4fa7add","tid":1215720,"uid":121387,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"09d93bdefe5e3e940185944a367ac3c95247236a","tid":1215720,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":21,"score":-21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T08:05:17.000Z","msg":"希望只係個asso 仔啦<br />\n<br />\n大學生留案底就乜前途都無晒"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T08:06:26.000Z","msg":"收皮啦仲講笑"}]}